docstring:
r"""
    Find unnamed groups in `pattern` and replace them with '<var>'. E.g.,
    1. ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/(\w+)$ ==> ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/<var>$
    2. ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/((x|y)\w+)$ ==> ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/<var>$
    3. ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/(\w+) ==> ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/<var>
    4. ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/((x|y)\w+) ==> ^(?P<a>\w+)/b/<var>
    """
name: replace_unnamed_groups
